lied to my face about Daniel.

11
00:00:27,453 --> 00:00:28,479
I quit.

12
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:29,840
Where's Daniel?

13
00:00:29,854 --> 00:00:31,278
He disappeared.

14
00:00:36,589 --> 00:00:40,182
Look, mija, I know you're upset
about leaving that big New York job,

15
00:00:40,198 --> 00:00:42,401
but you have to eat something.

16
00:00:42,827 --> 00:00:46,592
I never should have taken that
stupid position at Sofia's magazine.

17
00:00:46,608 --> 00:00:48,292
I should've just
stayed at "Mode."

18
00:00:48,305 --> 00:00:49,700
Yeah, aunt Betty.

19
00:00:50,095 --> 00:00:51,883
I miss the swag.

20
00:00:54,347 --> 00:00:58,512
Okay. Is there a sign on my
forehead that says, "crap here"?

21
00:00:59,575 --> 00:01:00,963
What's the matter with you?

22
00:01:00,977 --> 00:01:03,032
There's been an
Herbalux recall.

23
00:01:03,036 --> 00:01:06,300
They're pulling all the products just
'cause some housewives in Secaucus

24
