they put in their shampoo?

26
00:01:10,045 --> 00:01:11,712
They were using the hand cream.

27
00:01:11,725 --> 00:01:14,882
The F.D.A.
is recalling the whole line.

28
00:01:14,918 --> 00:01:16,572
I don't have a job anymore!

29
00:01:16,587 --> 00:01:17,661
Are you serious?

30
00:01:17,675 --> 00:01:19,541
Maybe Oprah can adopt us.

31
00:01:19,558 --> 00:01:21,861
Wait a minute.
I used that hand cream.

32
00:01:21,878 --> 00:01:25,472
Ay, what am I gonna do?
I have bills, car payments...

33
00:01:25,486 --> 00:01:27,931
These nails--
they don't just happen.

34
00:01:27,945 --> 00:01:29,443
I know how you feel.

35
00:01:29,457 --> 00:01:32,222
- When I left "Mode"--
- Ay, Betty! Please.

36
00:01:32,235 --> 00:01:34,100
Enough with the
"when I left 'Mode'"!

37
00:01:34,115 --> 00:01:36,163
Okay? This is
totally different.

38
00:01:36,178 --> 00:01:37,663
Herbalux was all I had.

39
00:01:37,678 --> 00:01:40,003
